          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_8"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>44 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The </span>Territorial<span style="color:#000000"> extent of the Act is England and Wales. Taxi and private hire legislation is devolved in Scotland and Northern Ireland.</span></p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="0.68in 0.82in 0.82in 0.82in 0.82in">
